{"service_name": "IBM Energy Management & Optimisation Services", "service_id": "7846747967045765", "company_name": "IBM United Kingdom Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     IBM United Kingdom Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     IBM Energy Management &amp; Optimisation Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Services include:\r\n\u2022\tEnergy Strategy to help organisations better manage their energy through improved data collection, analysis, information management, visualisation and collaboration.\r\n\u2022\tEnergy Planning to translate strategies into a cohesive programme of actionable initiatives.\r\n\u2022\tEnergy Analytics through deployment of analytics tools, applications and models to provide business benefit.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Real-time insight into energy performance across the estate\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Monitor and control energy systems/tasks through mobile devices\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Integration with building/external data (e.g. occupancy, lighting, weather)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Validation and verification of billing against actual consumption\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Alerts raised when energy systems show undesired condition/performance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Automated work-orders to respond to asset failure/sub-optimal performance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Forecasting future energy / carbon costs through complex modelling\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Scalable solutions for all sizes of organisations/growth agendas\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Solutions designed to take organisations through the maturity cycle\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Experienced industry/technology experts with support from global network\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Real-time insights into energy performance through mobile devices\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identification of best practice and prioritisation of future improvements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Optimise building behaviour (e.g. heating) based on data analytics\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Better decision making from complex forecasting models\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Prioritise options to reduce carbon emissions / costs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Immediate response to sub-optimal performance / maintenance requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Focus workforces effort where biggest gains can be realised\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Predictive analytics to respond to issues before they happen\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improve asset performance, reliability and longevity\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Flexibly enhancing  scope of energy solutions as organisation matures\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3375 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7846747967045765-pricing-document-2015-10-01-1345.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7846747967045765-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-01-1345.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7846747967045765-service-definition-document-2015-09-27-1706.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92284/7846747967045765-terms-and-conditions-2015-10-05-1106.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vii\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 7\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      7846\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      7479\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      6704\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      5765\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation